import React from "react"; const Middle = () => (

Set up your Wallet

Click get NFT and login to your metamask account using random message and connect your wallet.

Pick up your NFT that you like

Pick your NFT you want to send it to Lamose for engraving it on objects such as bottles, cups etc

Click send NFT to Lamose

After selecting your NFT, send NFT metadata to Lamose after paying some gas amount.

Get your NFT Engraved on objects

You will receive your Engraved object from Lamose soon after sending your NFT metadata to them.

); export default Middle;
